Bow, bow, says the dog;
              \nMew, mew, says the cat;
              \nGrunt, grunt, goes the hog;
              \nAnd squeak goes the rat.
              \nTu-whu, says the owl;
              \nCaw, caw, says the crow;
              \nQuack, quack, says the duck;
              \nAnd what the sparrow says,you know.
